The '''Christian Alliance Party''' is a [[political party]] in the [[Solomon Islands]]. At the [[Solomon Islands general election, 2006]], the party received 3,613 votes (1.9% of the total) and won no seats.

It did not contest the [[Solomon Islands general election, 2014|2014 general election]].

