'''Leonardo Mario Bernacch''' (January 5, 1935 – April 10, 2012) was the [[Roman Catholic]] [[titular bishop]] of '''Tabaicara''' and bishop of the [[Apostolic Vicariate of Camiri|Roman Catholic Apostolic Vicariate  of Camiri]], [[Bolivia]].

Ordained to the priesthood in 1958, Bernacchi became bishop in 1993 and retired in 2009.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bbernl.html Leonardo Mario Bernacchi]</ref>

